03:01:04,719 --> 03:01:07,420
you know, and it's people are very, people are very scared.

2110
03:01:07,740 --> 03:01:25,363
So I think and what we saw in Worcester last week, and how Worcester police handled that abhorrently, and is now pushing what I consider to be a pretty reactionary administration in the city of Worcester to consider a city policy about what the city will do in response to this.

2111
03:01:25,923 --> 03:01:30,784
I think for folks who have said that they are

2112
03:01:32,018 --> 03:01:43,300
on board with this, I think we need to be doing the same and have a very clear policy about this, how the city responds to federal intimidation and abuse of power, as well as informing the public about it.

2113
03:01:43,480 --> 03:01:49,042
And I know that public health and community safety brought up some of these concerns last week.

2114
03:01:49,062 --> 03:01:50,362
I don't know if you guys want to add anything.

2115
03:01:50,382 --> 03:01:51,542
I see Councilor Zaro.

2116
03:01:53,522 --> 03:01:54,583
Thank you.

2117
03:01:54,603 --> 03:01:57,523
I appreciate this conversation.

2118
03:01:57,543 --> 03:02:01,084
And I think there is more discussion to have

2119
03:02:02,327 --> 03:02:25,625
there are limitations to what our public safety officers will be able to do is my understanding, but I also know that we as local elected officials and local leaders have an obligation to

2120
03:02:27,197 --> 03:02:29,838
do what we can to try to keep our residents safe.

2121
03:02:30,119 --> 03:02:33,460
So that's been at the forefront of my mind for a long time.

2122
03:02:34,621 --> 03:02:38,523
And that means like physical safety and psychological safety.

2123
03:02:39,183 --> 03:02:49,188
So I continue to grapple with that, with how best to try to achieve that for our residents.

2124
03:02:49,628 --> 03:02:56,392
And I think that there's,

2125
03:02:57,525 --> 03:03:18,100
definitely more to be done within our local government and in our communities in mutual aid ways that do not participate in the hierarchy of law enforcement because there are limitations to that.

2126
03:03:19,621 --> 03:03:27,287
