2142
03:05:01,564 --> 03:05:03,805
I really think that everybody's intentions about this are good.

2143
03:05:05,366 --> 03:05:13,489
But I think that we have to keep in mind that a response can look like a lot of things and be more helpful than what it is right now.

2144
03:05:14,329 --> 03:05:22,153
I think that there is a very... I think that, you know, it's kind of trite,

2145
03:05:23,878 --> 03:05:28,759
Inaction is action, and I think that's what we have to be wary of when it comes to what we are declining to do.

2146
03:05:29,419 --> 03:05:35,101
