2152
03:06:10,161 --> 03:06:10,902
What are you doing here?

2153
03:06:10,922 --> 03:06:12,844
Is this okay?

2154
03:06:12,864 --> 03:06:13,705
This seems suspicious.

2155
03:06:13,745 --> 03:06:15,747
Let's make sure the people in the neighborhood are okay.

2156
03:06:16,247 --> 03:06:21,653
Because our local government has not taken on the onus of doing that community safety work.

2157
03:06:21,713 --> 03:06:22,674
And I think that needs to change.

2158
03:06:22,714 --> 03:06:26,258
I think we need to share that responsibility with the community, obviously.

2159
03:06:26,358 --> 03:06:30,682
And we share the responsibility of, if ICE has been present in the community,

2160
03:06:31,683 --> 03:06:36,026
