2161
03:06:36,066 --> 03:06:36,967
What do people need now?

2162
03:06:37,027 --> 03:06:37,607
Are people good?

2163
03:06:37,647 --> 03:06:38,247
What do they need?

2164
03:06:38,267 --> 03:06:39,048
Do they know their rights?

2165
03:06:40,609 --> 03:06:45,812
Is there support that's needed in the wake of being visited by ICE?

2166
03:06:45,852 --> 03:06:47,073
And it goes further than that as well.

2167
03:06:47,153 --> 03:06:49,295
But what I think is really unacceptable is to say,

2168
03:06:50,916 --> 03:06:55,240
Our responsibility is to do nothing and pretend that that's enough because it obviously isn't.

2169
03:06:55,320 --> 03:06:59,264
So I thank community members for leading the way here.

2170
03:06:59,484 --> 03:07:08,493
